OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry with sunny then clear spells on
OL,7,Fthe west coast. Becoming increasingly
OL,8,Fcloudy elsewhere through the evening
OL,9,Fand overnight with the odd spot of
OL,10,Flight drizzle possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely cloudy start with
OL,13,Fsome patchy light drizzle in east, but
OL,14,Fbright around the west coast.
OL,15,FGradually brightening up in the
OL,16,Fafernoon, best of the sunshine across
OL,17,FArgyll. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
